==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underlayer
<hw>Un"der*lay`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, underlays or is underlaid; a lower layer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>A perpendicular shaft sunk to
cut the lode at any required depth.</def> <rj><au>Weale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underleaf</ent>⟦br⟧
